* [x] `papirus-icon-theme`

### ‚úÖ Config files ready

* [x] Kvantum config present (`/etc/skel/.config/Kvantum/` ‚Üí MateriaDark)
* [x] GTK config present (`Breeze-Dark` + Papirus in skel)
* [x] Qt config present (`qt5ct`/`qt6ct` in skel; platform theme is **not** forced globally)
* [x] Theme selector present (menu + Desktop shortcut; **user-only** config writes)

üëâ Goal:

* looks good by default
